\subsection{ml_probit prediction types}{

The \code{type} argument controls what quantity is returned. Behavior differs
depending on whether the model is homoskedastic or heteroskedastic.\tabular{llll}{
   Type \tab Homoskedastic case \tab Heteroskedastic case \tab Notes \cr
